{"tid":672891,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"事實上我不相信人有自由意志","createTime":"2018-05-21T11:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T12:12:57.000Z","uid":187738,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f1617ae3b503228fc703429d57caa0ce3b39d61c","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"事實上我不相信人有自由意志<br />\n簡單來說，人每一分一秒都在吸收資訊 慢慢會進入你的潛意識，變成畫面。在你下次見到類似畫面時會LOAD出來左右你的決定。這是DYMANIC和INTERACTION的，內在與外界的不停互動，所以是PATH DEPENDENCE，你的任何一個反應也能從歷史中找到解釋。 <br />\n但我看過有人說 只要深入自己的潛意識，便能改變你的思想，命運，我不知道這對不對。 至少我現階反沒有這個能力做這種事。"},{"pid":"dc68236ac127d0e042b6cbcd2f6b75d2b9205140","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"在人類世界所有事都是二元性 DURABLE<br />\n這個我好像有點明白，又好像未完全掌握。"},{"pid":"7b696b86c8c00bb0875e3884af4b0c22d53b9f19","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc68236ac127d0e042b6cbcd2f6b75d2b9205140","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"在人類世界所有事都是二元性 DURABLE<br />\n這個我好像有點明白，又好像未完全掌握。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"二元論＝相對概念<br />\n目的，幫助我們理解一樣事物<br />\nEG。， 冷熱 舒服痛。。 我又明左小小了"},{"pid":"ead59ff0c02a42bac38adc6c3ffb6c4038796268","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"當你發現整個社會都在不停懷念的時候，你就知道這個社會很大獲。<br />\n在下降車九當中<br />\n又不見韓國係咁？哈哈"},{"pid":"a2eb5712f49f22fddb36a97acd1190489037f53c","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ead59ff0c02a42bac38adc6c3ffb6c4038796268","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"當你發現整個社會都在不停懷念的時候，你就知道這個社會很大獲。<br />\n在下降車九當中<br />\n又不見韓國係咁？哈哈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:28:05.000Z","msg":"我打哈哈的時候 面部是沒表情的， 這。。。"},{"pid":"40814f91501c860a7e47c7df5ef2b93a35bce103","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:32:33.000Z","msg":"我想像的他在旁-0度<br />\n他真實存在在溫哥華-1度<br />\n<br />\n0度和一度的分別<br />\n1-多了肉體（如眼球）的感知<br />\n2-沒有<br />\n<br />\n跳脫維度的方法<br />\n0+肉體感知度=1 肉體感知度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這樣可以超越時空<br />\n但1度求遠是base<br />\n1度肉體照有被影響<br />\n1度時間過去，你肉體都會消滅"},{"pid":"d9e92bf190e2979cb15dc5564d5c61342acaf05e","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/193522_8af14b223b0b690d5c80e8f52aeab3e4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F193522_8af14b223b0b690d5c80e8f52aeab3e4.JPG&h=ceb27808&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa60de5323f22a33c81adc47acc1f77c544cbada","tid":672891,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9e92bf190e2979cb15dc5564d5c61342acaf05e","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/193522_8af14b223b0b690d5c80e8f52aeab3e4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F193522_8af14b223b0b690d5c80e8f52aeab3e4.JPG&h=ceb27808&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21848825fe2ba8d81535996057a298ef781d5098","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa60de5323f22a33c81adc47acc1f77c544cbada","tid":672891,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9e92bf190e2979cb15dc5564d5c61342acaf05e","tid":672891,"uid":187738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/